Program: Discovery
Title: Viruses with an overcoat
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwtw
Last Broadcast Date: 03 March 1997
The genetic manipulation of plants and how viruses with 'overcoats' can produce proteins. Overcoat protein technology allows scientists to manipulate plants using harmless large viruses. Also in the programme using maths to help conserve water, junk DNA and why scientists might be becoming too specialised for their own good. Show less